Comment: 0,0:00:00.02,0:00:00.02,Comment,,0,0,0,,——Text——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.56,0:00:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,如果要下的話  倒是希望能在早上就開始下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.66,0:02:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,伊萬莉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.90,0:02:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.54,0:02:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.36,0:02:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼  只是覺得雨下得很大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.00,0:02:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,難道你沒帶傘嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.24,0:02:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是我疏忽大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.12,0:02:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,要我借你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.36,0:02:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,借給我  你用什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,難道你是二刀流?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.98,0:02:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我只帶了一把傘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.80,0:02:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我還要幫老師做事  所以暫時還不回去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.18,0:02:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,而且在我完事之後  這時雨應該就會停了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.78,0:02:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,聽說這雨會越下越大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.88,0:02:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道明天操場還能不能用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.54,0:02:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒事  你不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.20,0:02:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然我似乎是偏火屬性
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.18,0:02:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,所以可能會被人懷疑雨是我的弱點屬性
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.14,0:02:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,別看我這樣  其實我水屬性也挺不錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:03:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我從來都沒有擔心過這個方面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.08,0:03:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\b0\bord0\shad0\c&H404040&\frz331.6\pos(1254,607.5)}這樣子啊~~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.08,0:03:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\b0\bord0\shad0\c&H404040&\frz329.7\pos(769.5,751.5)}師傅、一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.46,0:03:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,可蕾說和我一起回去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.56,0:03:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎  真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.60,0:03:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.06,0:03:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,可蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.98,0:03:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐美學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.04,0:03:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我買了河童雨衣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.86,0:03:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,這顏色真好看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.28,0:03:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.30,0:03:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,伊萬莉在等你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.18,0:03:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那我得抓緊了  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.40,0:03:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.92,0:03:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,河童?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.90,0:03:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,今天是你值日嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,算是吧  內卷要回去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.20,0:03:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.92,0:03:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,要我幫忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.48,0:03:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.86,0:03:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,內卷你有帶傘嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.38,0:03:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那你帶伊萬莉一起撐回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.20,0:04:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,她沒有帶傘  非常頭痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,她現在應該還在樓梯口那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.46,0:04:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,這倒也是  這麼大雨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.26,0:04:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.18,0:04:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,武田老師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.88,0:04:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,收上來的筆記本我就放在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.80,0:04:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐美  麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.36,0:04:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.68,0:04:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你要喝咖啡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.84,0:04:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不用了  我還要收拾一下東西  就先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.75,0:05:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎  那能麻煩你幫忙補充一下粉筆嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.44,0:05:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,就在器材室右邊那個架子上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.60,0:05:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,看來還要花點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.32,0:05:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞瑞  瑞瑞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是薰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.66,0:05:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,其實我今天差點遲到  所以忘記帶傘了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.86,0:05:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,人家很可憐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.78,0:05:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼好意思說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  瑞瑞你的傘我就借走了哇~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.78,0:05:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,給我等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.84,0:05:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,別隨便給我拿走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.74,0:05:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,原諒我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.46,0:05:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我這絕對不能原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.76,0:05:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,薰!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺禍不單行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.14,0:06:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,薰那傢伙  居然真帶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你終於來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.10,0:06:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,內卷?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,伊萬莉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.10,0:06:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,這個的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.00,0:06:58.28,Comment,,0,0,0,,伊萬莉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.72,0:06:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那之後我馬上來到這裡找她  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.12,0:07:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.22,0:07:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,伊萬莉同學  你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,伊萬莉同學?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.26,0:07:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,這是雨水
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.88,0:07:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,亦或是淚水呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.02,0:07:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,亞爾希安戰記第二章  是和馬莉安娜訣別的場景
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.54,0:07:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,正確
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.10,0:07:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,才不對  你這樣會感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.00,0:07:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,內卷  你可別小瞧我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.52,0:07:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我可是有水之精靈的加護
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.24,0:07:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,伊萬莉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.52,0:07:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,伊萬莉同學!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.66,0:07:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,師傅  等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.32,0:07:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,可蕾特同學  原來你也在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.10,0:07:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這種情況
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.80,0:07:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,真像那兩個人會搞出的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.24,0:07:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,然後為什麼你會留下來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.68,0:08:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,當然是在等你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.14,0:08:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你朋友把你的傘借走了不是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.32,0:08:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞瑞就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.10,0:08:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,內卷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.90,0:08:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b0\bord0\shad0\c&H453A38&\move(462,310.5,522,340.5)}薰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.04,0:08:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,薰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.56,0:08:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,要和我一起用這把傘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.00,0:08:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.52,0:08:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,薰  謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.52,0:08:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.12,0:08:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.20,0:08:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.08,0:08:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,打…打擾了…
